# Automated Lead Follow-Up System — DFW Service Businesses

An end-to-end lead capture and follow-up automation built for local DFW service businesses that run on leads and appointments and can't afford to let one slip through the cracks.

## What It Does

The second a prospect fills out a contact form, this system fires automatically — no human needed:

1. **Instant personalized email** sent to the lead confirming their inquiry
2. **Business hours detection** — system responds differently based on time of day/after hours
3. **Instant owner notification** with full lead details delivered immediately
4. **Automatic lead logging** — every contact is tracked and stored
5. **Automated follow-up** — if the lead hasn't responded in 2 hours, a follow-up email goes out on its own

Zero manual work. Runs 24/7 while the business owner is on the job.

